abstract: >-
  AstrBot — an open-source all-in-one Agent chatbot platform. Integrates with QQ, WeChat Work, Feishu, DingTalk, WeChat OA, Telegram, Slack and more. LLM conversations, multimodal, Agent, MCP, Skills, knowledge base, persona, 1000+ plugins, isolated Agent Sandbox, i18n.
